title: How do i enter the pixel art comp
body:

replies.body:
The OCE Pixel Art Contest submission period ended on the 10th of this month, as per [the official post.](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-creations/28E6ZOUG-pixel-art-contest)

Let me know if you have any questions.
